“Same mean unna datasets kuda consistency different ga untayi. Variance/SD spread and uncertainty ni capture chestayi. Scaling, anomaly detection, feature analysis lo useful.”

## Hypothesis Testing
“Observed lift actual effect aa leka random fluctuation aa ani test cheyyadaniki use chestham. But p-value ni business impact tho kalipi interpret cheyyali.”

## Bayes
“Prior belief ni new evidence tho update cheyyadam. Rare-event problems and class imbalance understanding ki chala important.”

## Linear Algebra
“ML operations scalable ga, vectorized ga, GPU-friendly ga perform cheyyadaniki linear algebra core foundation.”

## Gradient Descent
“Loss landscape lo parameters ni iterative ga update chesi error minimize chese process.”

## Bias-Variance
“Model simplicity and sensitivity madhya tradeoff. Generalization target chesthe balance important.”

